Package org.directwebremoting.json.types Description

This package includes an implementation of the JSON spec in Java.

The JSON spec includes the types object, array, number, string and boolean. All of these types have objects to represent them however JsonValue has getters to allow you to get at the more natural types with ease. The object and array types are implemented especially by JsonObject and JsonArray.
